  "title": "Senior Executive (Design & Content) #JTL",
  "description": "<ul><li>Manage social media platforms, including content planning, posting schedules, website and Intranet updates and website revamp.</li><li>Develop engaging, audience-focused content, including student stories, research highlights, event promotions, and scholarship features.</li><li>Design and produce marketing materials in a variety of formats, including print, video, and digital platforms.</li><li>Support outreach initiatives and events management, including postgraduate events, career fairs, and information sessions.</li><li>Provide administrative support on partnership matters\nand related activities.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements </strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Degree in Mass Communications, Visual Communications, Graphic Design or a related field.</li><li>Excellent writing, design and visual marketing skills with 2 to 3 years’ working experience in design, video production or marcoms.</li></ul><p><strong>Interested candidates please send in your resume to:</strong><br /><strong>Topaz Liang Humin (CEI No. R1104500), email to: west5@recruitexpress.com.sg </strong><br /><strong>EA License No.:99C4599</strong></p>",
